text: Ingen may refer to: * Ingen Ryuki (1592-1673), Buddhist monk * Ingen, Netherlands, a village * InGen, a fictional genetics company from Jurassic Park * a part of Irish names like in Sabdh ingen Gluniarainn mac Murchada, abbess of Kildare since 1132 * Van Ingen (surname), a Dutch surname ==See also== * NGEN (disambiguation) * Engine (disambiguation) * * *
title: Ingen (disambiguation)
